		<div  id="headers">
			<strong>Description</strong>
		</div>
		<br />
		This fast-paced project-oriented course is centered around application development 
		on the iOS platform. The first half of the course will involve the fundamentals 
		of iPhone development, where students learn Objective-C, as well as 
		efficient memory management and event-based programming on the iOS platform. 
		<br /><br />
		In the second half of the course, students work in teams to conceptualize and
		develop a significant iPhone application. To aid in this process, we will be 
		teaching you the basics of creating a backend enabling you to create server-client applications.
		<br /><br />
		Creativity and originality are highly encouraged!
		<br /><br /><br />


		<div id="headers">
