		We are excited to say that this course has 
		a hint of entrepreneurship weaved into it as well!
		It is taught by iPhone Dev and Angel Investor, 
		<a href="http://jimy.org" class="link" target="_blank">Jim Young</a>.
		One of the main goals of the course is to get that final project into the AppStore!
		<br /><br />
		The students in the 
		<a class="link" target="_blank" href="http://www.stanford.edu/class/cs193p/cgi-bin/drupal/" title="CS 193P iPhone Application Development">Stanford iPhone class</a> have had their apps
		downloaded many times and an app made in an 
		<a class="link" target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/cs3217">iPad class in Singapore</a>
		has made two-hundred-thousand dollars!
